title: Armstrong-Who or What is Prophetic Beast?(1960)
description: This is Herbert W. Armstrong&#039;s amazing booklet Who or What is the Prophetic Beast? (1960) which investigates the identity of the biblical "beast" of the Apocalypse in book of Revelation. What does Bible prophecy reveal about world events now leading to Armageddon and the end of this age? This two-part booklet deals with governments and wars that will bring this world to its final end. Includes 2nd part called The Mark of the Beast . . . It is Here Now! (1952). 50 pages, some illustrations. A must read for everyone.
